{"tid":1784202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拍片誦詩 為港人打氣","createTime":"2019-12-15T13:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T13:27:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9f98f058e76b4389be7fffd01a918753d0fbc1","tid":1784202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191214/6ZQZPNBRYYJMSHPGUG3Z7LEYYM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191214%2F6ZQZPNBRYYJMSHPGUG3Z7LEYYM%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=2dd0b1e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191214%2F6ZQZPNBRYYJMSHPGUG3Z7LEYYM%2F&h=7970bb4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191214/6ZQZPNBRYYJMSHPGUG3Z7LEYYM/</a><br />\n<br />\n拍片誦詩 為港人打氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191214/large/1576253956_f7ad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576253956_f7ad.gif&h=cd9120a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n耶魯大學戲劇系畢業後，郭佳怡醉心於舞台劇創作。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】郭佳怡拍攝的「2047」短片，構思來自她上月18日受邀在紐約的詩人咖啡館進行朗詩表演，當時原打算朗讀早就寫好的舊詩，最後她改變主意，決定為香港發聲，前一夜遂創作了新詩，後來朋友提議製成影片，由於當日剛好是反送中逆權運動第162天，她亦在短片特別提及。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港台新聞部超支 反面臨削資源<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n向中國挑機<br />\n<br />\n短片中她提及香港警察的濫暴情況，包括全港600多萬市民一同承受萬枚的催淚彈、海綿彈、布袋彈、橡膠子彈及實彈的威脅，她看過無數抗爭香港人受傷的影片，「每天早上，我醒來都看到自己頭破血流的新聞」。<br />\n<br />\n惟雖然如此，郭佳怡仍向中國「下戰書」，說：「放馬過來吧中國&hellip;&hellip;令我消失吧，只因我用了醜陋但準確的字眼！」（Go ahead China, make me disappeared, arrest me for the ugly, accurate words！）再用廣東話稱：「我唔怕死㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n短片後部所讀出的一首名為「2047」的詩，郭佳怡以英文誦讀時，以廣東話穿插加入「香港人加油！香港人不放棄！」的句子，明言希望所有美國人聚焦香港這小島，並說出：「我們與你同行，我們一定會支持保護你！」的諾言。"},{"pid":"b84d16346ffa5cea3ea6ccba1615c0ca8218159e","tid":1784202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDHdKiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDHdKiw.jpg&h=779c8437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e91bbd63a441144f3c416dff3cf039259c5258b","tid":1784202,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">德國戰線要人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6fe42ae84e3e3f0a87ea81f84c096d13986c86ef","tid":1784202,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}